snippet.title: WarioWare Gold – Launch Trailer (Nintendo 3DS)
snippet.description:
The zigzag-'stached man is back and better than ever in WarioWare Gold, out now! Mash, twist, touch, and blow in 300 microgames and win Wario's greatest video game tournament!

Official Website: http://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-3DS/WarioWare-Gold-1348073.html?utm_medium=social&utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=WarioWareGold%7CLaunch%7Cw30
